<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ل س ع:</span> <span class="c2">(لَسَعَتْهُ)</span> الْعَقْرَبُ وَالْحَيَّةُ مِنْ بَابِ قَطَعَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[لسق، لصق]</span> ل س ق،<span class="c5"> ل ص ق:</span> <span class="c2">(لَسِقَ)</span> بِهِ وَ <span class="c2">(لَصِقَ)</span> بِهِ بِالْكَسْرِ <span class="c2">(لُصُوقًا)</span> بِالضَّمِّ وَ <span class="c2">(الْتَسَقَ)</span> بِهِ وَ <span class="c2">(الْتَصَقَ)</span> بِهِ وَ <span class="c2">(أَلْسَقَهُ)</span> بِهِ غَيْرُهُ وَ <span class="c2">(أَلْصَقَهُ)</span> بِهِ غَيْرُهُ. وَفُلَانٌ <span class="c2">(لِسْقِي)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(لِصْقِي)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(بِلِسْقِي)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(بِلِصْقِي)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(لَسِيقِي)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(لَصِيقِي)</span> أَيْ بِجَنْبِي كُلُّهُ بِمَعْنًى وَاحِدٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>